Try planting your finger ahead of the path of the drone_ and the little fella will fly right into you. Crash! ðŸ’¥
For all the "don't tap" advice that folks give_ it really does feel satisfying to tap an elite drone out of the air. Just press it right out of the sky
When I first started_ I missed the regular drones so consistently that I thought they weren't actually separate objects. Gave up on them for a while
When there isn't a contract or a soul egg multiplier event running_ I check in about once a day to refresh the doubler and collect the daily gift
If you play long enough_ you get to a point where there isn't much left to do
One clever secret of the game is_ no matter which egg you're on_ you're actually farming soul eggs. Prestiging is a core mechanic of the game_ and you shouldn't be afraid to do it
